*ghemical-1.90 (09 Jul 2005)

  09 Jul 2005; Donnie Berkholz <spyderous@gentoo.org>;
  +files/ghemical-1.90-ghemical-server-fix.patch,
  +files/1.90-gcc3.4-r1.patch, +ghemical-1.90.ebuild:
